tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE properties (id INT PRIMARY KEY, property_name STRING, owner_id INT REFERENCES owners(id), tenant_id INT REFERENCES tenants(id));

CREATE TABLE owner_properties (
    owner_id INT,
    property_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (owner_id, property_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (owner_id) REFERENCES owners(owner_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES properties(property_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tenant_properties (
    tenant_id INT,
    property_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (tenant_id, property_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (tenant_id) REFERENCES tenants(tenant_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES properties(property_id)
);
